headline: PulteGroup Named to the Fortune 100 Best Companies to Work For® List for Fifth Consecutive Year
summary: ATLANTA, April 02, 2025--For the fifth consecutive year, Great Place To Work® and Fortune magazine have recognized PulteGroup (NYSE: PHM) as one of the Fortune 100 Best Companies to Work For® in 2025. This year, PulteGroup ranks 47th, demonstrating Pulte's dedication to creating a workplace where employees thrive through meaningful collaboration, innovation, and shared success.
